Freshdirect Logo
FreshDirect is an online grocery delivery service in the United States. Initially established in New York City, the company expanded to include much of the New York Metropolitan area as well as select counties in New Jersey, Connecticut, Pennsylvania, Delaware and the Washington, DC metro area. FreshDirect custom-packages groceries and meals for its customers using just-in-time manufacturing, a practice that reduces waste, and improves quality and freshness. The company offers its services via a website and mobile app.
You can download theFreshdirectlogo on full-version of the page.
